x, y = 10, 20
v1 = Vector2D(x, y)
self._check_vector(v1, x, y)
v1 = Vector2D((x, y))
self._check_vector(v1, x, y)
v1 = Vector2D([x, y])
self._check_vector(v1, x, y)
self.assertEqual(v1, v1.clone())
for angle in (20, 60, 100, 180):
    v1 = Vector2D.from_angle(angle)
    self.assertAlmostEqual(v1.orientation, angle)
    v1 = Vector2D.from_angle(-angle)
    self.assertAlmostEqual(v1.orientation, -angle)
